description:
Kamineko (「噛み猫」, "Biting Cat", or "Evil Cat" in Japanese) is a gray cat that http://anidb.net/ch7480 [Sakaki] occasionally sees on the way to and from school. Having a great soft spot for cats, Sakaki tries to pet it, but it ends up latching its huge, beartrap-like teeth onto her hand.
Source: http://azumanga.wikia.com/wiki/Kamineko
name: Kamineko
